title: Guo Guo Qi Xia Chuan
synopsis: "The Legend of Guoguo Rider" tells the story of a flower-giving young Guoguo, who obtained a magical power because of an accident. Facing threats to their homeland, Guoguo and his friends stepped forward to take on the important task of maintaining peace on the island. For this reason, they had to embark on a journey to collect five energy stones before the dark forces. After experiencing a series of difficulties, contradictions, misunderstandings, and shortages of materials, the friends finally worked together to destroy the darkness. Sir's evil conspiracy...(translated from douban)

title: Dongbei Hua Ze Lei Zhi Qi Yao Ezi
synopsis: The story takes place in an old industrial city in the northeast that is undergoing transformation. The down-to-earth miner, Diaosi Lao Gen, longs for a stable love and life. After reluctantly paying his sincerity, he always encounters a green tea bitch who is climbing the dragon and the phoenix. Lao Gen’s friend Hua Ze Lei is an idealistic internet addiction nerd. In order to appease Lao Gen, who is broken in love, he proposes to relax in the bath center. Unexpectedly, the masseur they met during the period turned out to be Lao Gen’s third aunt... (translated from douban)

title: Gulu Gulu Meirenyu
synopsis: A Hulu Island where ancient civilization and future technology coexist. 　　 A dead and cute little mermaid Gulu was rescued by the human boy Yuball, and began their life of intertwined fate and fun. 　　 A journey full of thrills, fantasy and joy is about to begin. Can the Little Mermaid escape every trap? How does the fish ball protect the magic trick from the ocean? (translated from douban)

title: Gulu Gulu Meirenyu 2

title: Wudi Xiao Fei Zhu
synopsis: The protagonist Ling Fei is a little daughter with a slight "princess disease" who was sent by her parents to a weird training camp to spend the summer vacation. In this weird training camp, Ling Fei met the computer prodigy Ai Ding, and the two quickly became good friends; 　　 One night, Ling Fei came out for a walk alone, and ran into a little flying pig falling from the sky. Ling Fei thought it was cute and took it back to the dorm. From then on, Ling Fei took the little flying pig to participate in various activities of the training camp. 　　 One day Little Flying Pig broke into Professor Gulafa's laboratory and messed up with the professor. He felt that the professor's laboratory was very fun and planned to bring Ling Fei and the others to play together next time. At the same time, two alien bugs sent by the leader of the alien forces sneaked into the training camp, preparing to steal the space-time artifacts hidden in the professor's laboratory. Little Feizhu brought Ling Fei and others to the laboratory of Professor Gulafa, only to find that the professor was injured and he knew the true identity of the professor. It turns out that Gu Lafa is a magic teacher who has lived for thousands of years, and has always mastered the mission of guarding and opening the magic door of time and space! 　　Professor's selflessness infected the children, so Ling Fei and others decided to help the professor get back the safe containing space-time artifacts. In the end, with the help of the boundless little flying pig, the plan of the alien creatures completely fell through. The professor did not use violent means to deal with the two alien insects, but decided to open the door of time and space and send the alien insects back; after these waves, everyone in the training camp began to "grow up", and everyone got it. New enlightenment and perception. 　　 At the same time, Little Flying Pig also completed the "Angel Mission" assigned to him by the Pig Planet. Little Flying Pig looked at everyone reluctantly, and finally turned into a light to travel through the sky...(translated from douban)

title: San Zhi Xiao Zhu Yu Shen Deng
synopsis: Xiaomi (voiced by Li Ye), Dangdang (voiced by Wang Xiaotong) and Bobo (voiced by Hong Haitian) are friends who talk about everything in the kindergarten. The three little pigs who yearn for a free life naturally can't stand the many rules in the kindergarten. Want to sneak out to play. By chance, the three little pigs got a mysterious treasure map and pointed out the magic lamp that could help people realize their wishes. The three of them set off happily. 　　 In the end, the three Xiaozhi found the magic lamp, but found that the magic lamp could not be activated without the fire, so the three of them turned their goal to find the fire. On the way, the three met a little wolf named Shishilang (voiced by Wang Yanhua). It turned out that the treasure map was originally his treasure, but unfortunately it was lost and picked up by the pigs. Shijiro angrily vowed to take back the magic lamp that belonged to it, so the two parties started a contest against time. (translated from douban)

title: San Zhi Xiao Zhu Yu Gongfu Pan Da
synopsis: The three little pigs were naughty in distress and were rescued by Kung Fu heroes Apan and Ada, so the little pigs followed the two to learn kung fu. However, when the little pigs realized that the two heroes were not as powerful as they thought they were, they determined to defeat the Kung Fu monster wolves by their own strength, but their impulse and recklessness once again caused a greater disaster. The Kung Fu Wolves threatened with the three little pigs, forcing Apan and Ada to make another move. A peak duel of power and responsibility, justice and power, began in the forest kingdom. (translated from douban)

title: Baixue Gongzhu He San Zhi Xiao Zhu
synopsis: Snow White (voiced by Ni Hongjie) has a beautiful appearance and a kind personality, and is deeply loved by the people. The Snow Queen (voiced by Gu Zi) sends her to the Elf Kingdom, hoping she will live a happy life there. In an accident, Snow White accidentally fell off the cliff. Although she was not injured, she lost her memory. Chi Bao (voiced by Ma Xiaoji), Meng Bao (voiced by Ye Zixuan) and Pi Bao (voiced by Hu Jiamu) are three cute little pigs. They rescued Snow White who had nowhere to go and warmly invited her to live with them. In this way, Snow White and the cute three little pigs had a carefree happy time. The Snow Queen has been looking for Snow White’s traces. At the same time, the evil wolf grandmother (voiced by Ma Xiaoji) also sent her minions hunter (voiced by Chen Zhe) and Black Wolf (voiced by Zhao Mingzhou) to get ahead of the Snow Queen. Catch Snow White.(translated from douban)

title: San Zhi Xiao Zhu Zhi Mofa Da Maoxian
synopsis: Zhuzhu Kindergarten has three friends: Xiaomi, Dangdang and Bobo. They are adventurous and hate the unchanging life of kindergarten. In this way they began their adventure in the magical world. (translated from douban)

title: Chao Neng Tu Zhandui
synopsis: Humans left four rabbits on the moon. Fortunately, they were adopted by Chang'e. Chang'e is a standard "soil, fat and round", but she is good at changing appearance, always dressing herself up to deceive the world. The four rabbits and Chang'e depended on each other for their lives. Under the influence of the eyes and ears, the rabbits naturally "joined" and became Chang'e's accomplices. 　　 Big Bear Habi has always regarded Chang'e as the goddess in his heart. In order to see the goddess' true face, he would go to the moon in person, but found that Chang'e's face was very different from what he saw on the Internet. In a rage, Habi kidnapped Chang'e, hoping to teach her a lesson. The rabbits followed in the footsteps of their masters and came to the earth. Here they met a young man named Liangchawei. With the help of Liangchawei, the rabbits He learned the profound meanings and showed his supernatural powers, and finally rescued Chang'e.(translated from douban)

title: Jujinghuishen Bang
synopsis: The children were selected to receive training and study at the Shenyang Academy. Raised by his grandfather since childhood, Chen Xiaohu, who is outstanding and helpful, became good friends with Yan Xiaoqi, Cui Shao and others and entered the academy together. Through hard study and difficult tests, the students grow together. (translated from douban)

title: Ali Baba Dadao Qibing
synopsis: In the middle of the 15th century, the richest adventure kingdom on the Central Continent circulated a legend about the king's heart-as long as you find the king's heart, you can become a king. Princess Margina has never had a real adventure because of her cowardly nature. Everyone in the adventure kingdom knows her as the "coward princess". She has been working hard to inherit the throne, but she was questioned at the ball where the king announced her successor. She wanted to become the king and decided to prove herself. She escaped from the ball and became a partner with the slum boy Ali Baba. Together with Alibaba, his "Treasure Hunting Guide" entered the mysterious and exciting world of treasure trove and embarked on a journey to find the heart of the king. Entering the treasury with them is a trio of robbers who do no evil. They conquered the mirror monsters and formed a powerful gang of forty thieves. The robber boss wants to get the king's heart to establish a robber kingdom, and the unpredictable danger will face the princess and Ali. Baba approached step by step. 　　 In the end, the princess and her team passed the dangers of the treasure house, and Alibaba realized his wish to defeat the robbers. The princess got the heart of the king, and also understood the abilities most needed to become a king, and grew up in the adventure. (translated from douban)

title: Xinnian Lai La Zhi Da Nao Chuxi
synopsis: The evil New Year's Eve (voiced by Chen Zhao) accidentally got a mysterious scroll and made a pill that could control the Chinese zodiac. A group of people conquered the kingdom of sheep and sheep, and even attempted to take the opportunity to rule the world at the time of the new year. The king of the Sheep and Sheep Kingdom had no choice but to ask for help from the New Year (voiced by Yi Xiaoyin). After learning of the conspiracy on New Year’s Eve, the New Year rushed to the Sheep and Sheep Kingdom with his friends. 　　 Minister Lao Sheep told the New Year that the only thing that can defeat the New Year’s Eve is the four treasures who do not know where they are. The New Year promised to Princess Baa (voiced by Gong Dafang) that he would defeat the New Year’s Eve and save the sheep and sheep from the fire. Knowing that the New Year's Eve is looking for the Four Treasures, he naturally did not show weakness on New Year's Eve. He sent five horses and tail sheep, followed by a thrilling treasure hunt.(translated from douban)

title: Xinnian Lai La Zhi Yimingjingren
synopsis: During the New Year, I got along with the Spring girl, the younger brother and the zodiac animals in the village. I experienced true friendship and didn't want to return to New Year's Eve. Twelve pills were made on New Year's Eve, and every time one is eaten, it can be transformed into a zodiac animal. Driven by curiosity, the New Year began to take pills, learn to change, and follow the instructions of New Year's Eve to destroy the village. On New Year's Eve, I wanted to teach all my bad qualities, such as "blindness", "criticalness", "arrogance", "indifference", "greed", etc., to the New Year, but my friends around the New Year corrected it time and time again. During this period, under the expectation of everyone, the New Year brought rainwater to the arid village, encouraged the depressed friend Chenlong, retrieved the heirloom quyuan plough stolen on New Year’s Eve for the old cow, and helped the tail sheep. After completing the dream of becoming a singer and helping the lonely rabbit to meet friends, he did a lot of good things to help everyone. The friendship between New Year and everyone has also deepened step by step...(translated from douban)

In the New Year, I found the Kuixing of the Big Dipper, which controls all the writings in the world. On New Year's Eve, all the text spirits in the world were captured, causing everyone to become illiterate. After a series of searching and fighting, the New Year rescued the literary spirit and helped Kuixing rise to the night sky again, and Chinese characters returned to the world. Occasionally, Kudola discovered that the love of friends can be transformed into energy needed for spacecraft repair. For fear of everyone’s sadness, Kudola has never told everyone about going home. With their laughter and positive energy, they affect the people around them even more. The students and teachers with their own funny personality are all surrounded by the magical life locks of Xiaodi's family and gradually become their best friends and fans. , Qi released hilarious positive energy to reshape a happy and positive life attitude for the tense modern social life.(translated from douban)

synopsis: Zhou Xiaodi (voiced by Xu Jiao) and Dad Zhou (played by Shi Banyu), Alien Dog Qizai (voiced by Lin Yan), and Big Fat Dog Chocolate (voiced by Jian Yaozong) live a happy life together. One day, they met Alien Confusion Warrior 88 in an abandoned amusement park. The confused warrior told Zhou Xiaodi that at this time, the star demon King Jin Baobao (voiced by Ma Yufei) was about to move. It planned a conspiracy called "Dark Food Project" to dominate the earth by this, and the responsibility of the confused warrior was to defeat Golden baby, protect the earth. 　　 Zhou Xiaodi decided to help the confused warriors. They learned that a long-lost ancient book recorded the secret weapon that could defeat the golden baby, so the group embarked on a journey to find the ancient book. Along the way, what stories of laughter and tears await them? (translated from douban)

title: Xiao Zhu Ban Na
synopsis: "Little Pig Banner"] takes the Star Fantasy Island to nurture future fairy tale stars as the stage, tells the story of the cute, naughty and curious Little Pig Banner and his friends growing up with laughter and tears. Each episode has a small surprise, warm and loving People moved, without losing humor, let the audience and the piggy banner feel the happy sunshine together. 　　The story takes place in a mysterious place. This is a place full of innocence and childlikeness, which makes children most fascinated-Star Fantasy Island. Because the children's most familiar and favorite fairy tale characters come from this place. 　　 In order to fulfill his father’s wish, the cute Banner attended the fairy tale training class on Star Fantasy Island during the summer vacation, and the interesting story unfolded. Banner met many new partners on the Star Fantasy Island. They studied, lived, and played together under the guidance of the fairy tale training master Dr. Hai. There were conflicts, competition, cooperation, success, happiness, joy, and There are often some small pranks. Banner has a little rebellion and resistance from the beginning, and later learned what courage and responsibility are, and finally understands the importance of sincerity and friendship. It also made adults understand that children's growth requires careful care and patient nurturing. Each episode of the story will have a small surprise, warm, loving, and touching. (translated from douban)

title: Xiao Zhu Ban Na 2
synopsis: The happy and harmonious life on the Star Fantasy Island has caused a wave of dissatisfaction and covetousness from the evil forces. There is a mysterious magic island in the depths of the ocean. The owner of the island is the King of Snoring who has no laughter or happiness. It is precisely because the life of the Star Island is full of so much happiness, that angers the King of Snoring and is determined to disrupt their lives. . So he sent his men: Shuangshuang, Lost, and Risky to go to Star Fantasy Island to complete this difficult task. The troubles don't stop there. Dr. Hai’s old enemy is deadly, and Dr. Prawn, the owner of Kung Fu Island, has also coveted Star Fantasy Island for a long time. It seems that Star Fantasy Island is really facing a thorny problem, but don't forget that we still have the lovely Banner. The great difficulties will be solved in his play. Banner, this little guy, is not easy to mess with. In the end, the big bad guys can only steal the chicken instead of eroding the rice, causing all kinds of troubles and troubles for themselves, but also adding a lot of new things to the lives of Banner and his friends. fun of.(translated from douban)

synopsis: Because both, reckless and lost, the sabotage plan on the Star Fantasy Island would be cracked by Banner every time, the frustrated King Hulu decided to go out himself. An open gun battle, a good show of tearing down each other's stage was staged. (translated fropm baidu baike)

title: Xiao Zhu Ban Na Da Dianying Zhi Mengxiang Da “Mao” Xian
synopsis: When the summer vacation came, Banner accidentally learned that there is an old man with a magic hat in Magic Hat Island, who can make a magic hat to realize people's dreams. In order to realize the dream of adventurers, Banner and his friends set sail together to Magic Hat Island. However, the news was The villain Clown and General Meow discovered that they launched a series of evil obstruction operations. 　　 After a series of obstacles, Banner and others passed through the mysterious sea and finally came to Magic Hat Island and obtained the Magic Hat from the old man. Banner, wearing a magic sailor hat, also became a sea adventurer smoothly. However, at this time, General Joker and Meow stole the most powerful "pirate hat" on the island, defeated Banner, and took away the power of the sailor hat. 　　 In order to defeat the clown, Banner re-sews a new magic hat with magic gold thread with the help of the old man in the magic hat, and prepares to challenge the bad guys again. The pirate hat of the clown and the sailor hat of Banner launched a thrilling and endless "Magic Hat War". 　　 During the war, the pirate hat was very powerful. Banner was still lost and was shot into the sea. The whereabouts were unknown, and the partners were in trouble. At the moment of crisis, Banner, who was rescued by the flying fish or sea monster, finally defeated the clown through his own strength and the concerted efforts of his friends.(translated from douban)

synopsis: The traditional drama of "Wu Song Fighting Tiger" is staged in small theaters every day, but Li Duoduo, the actor of "Mechanical Cute Tiger", is unwilling to follow the rules every day and wants to become a Kung Fu star. In his free time performing in the small theater, he shuttled between the various studios to work harder for his dreams. Through his unremitting perseverance, Li Duoduo's talent was finally recognized by everyone, but he accidentally discovered that the sky was so shameful that his father, who was also a Kung Fu star, was in deep crisis. For justice and family affection, Li Duoduo and his former partner "Mechanical Cute Tiger" once again merged into a "Cute Tiger Agent" to challenge the dictator.(translated from douban)

synopsis: school started! school started! But what the hell is the sudden final exam? ! Cheating as much as you want, or just sit and die, Ajimid, let’s see your... Ajimeide fell in love with the goddess Meowsli at first sight during the final exams at the beginning of school. This time, Aji is about to start a love offensive against the goddess. Is he transformed into a warm boy or a scheming boy... confession one hundred Eight martial arts, watch Ajimeide's seventy-two changes! Aji and his friends decided to find an internship, but they encountered the hidden rules of the interview. Where should Aji go. When Aji decided to accept it painfully, they never expected... The Cucumber Art Institute was inexplicably covered by a layer of haze, and terrible ghost stories and legends spread throughout the campus. title: Baixue Gongzhu Zhi Shenmi Baba
synopsis: Hannah (voiced by Gao Mingjue) lost her father since childhood. Everyone said that he had gone to another world. Only Hannah firmly believed that her father was still alive. With a magical feather, Hannah embarked on a journey to find her father alone. She wanted to find the god bird, because the god bird knew the whereabouts of her father. 　　 In the midst of an accidental hit, Hannah broke into the wooden house of the dwarfs in the forest. Knowing Hannah's life experience, Snow White (voiced by Yan Mengmeng) and the dwarves were deeply moved and determined to help Hanna find her father. The group got on the hot air balloon and headed towards the bird island where the sacred bird lives. Along the way, Hannah and the others encountered natural and man-made disasters, but they did not stop moving forward. In the end, they arrived at their destination smoothly and learned that the disappearance of their father and the evil queen (voiced by Lin Lan) are unclear. relationship.(translated from douban)

title: Yaogun Cang Ao
synopsis: The Tibetan Mastiff Bodi (voiced by Guo Qilin) grew up in a mountain village. He was supposed to be the guardian of the village, but fell in love with modern rock music. In order to pursue his musical dream, he entered the city, failed to find a band, was frustrated with his apprenticeship, and was repeatedly calculated by wolves. However, he persisted, not only to save the villagers, but also to make up for the rift in his family, and finally his dream came true. (translated from douban)

synopsis: "Chinese New Year" is the most important thing for Chinese people throughout the year, and it is also the bond that maintains Chinese people's emotions. But the Nian Beast in Tiangong (voiced by Lei Jiayin) does not love the New Year! In order to cancel the Spring Festival, Nian Beast almost stabbed a big basket, he had to come to the world and met the little girl Sha Guo (voiced by Zhou Dongyu). The fantasy journey of a super villain and a rebellious little loli is about to begin, and a hilarious and hilarious comedy begins... (translated from douban)

details.Japanese: ある日本の絵描き少年

title: Shuumatsu no Walküre
synopsis: High above the realm of man, the gods of the world have convened to decide on a single matter: the continued existence of mankind. Under the head of Zeus, the deities of Ancient Greece, Norse mythology, and Hinduism, among others, call assembly every one thousand years to decide the fate of humanity. Because of their unrelenting abuse toward each other and the planet, this time the gods vote unanimously in favor of ending the human race. But before the mandate passes, Brunhild, one of the 13 demigod Valkyries, puts forth an alternate proposal: rather than anticlimactically annihilating mankind, why not give them a fighting chance and enact Ragnarök, a one-on-one showdown between man and god? Spurred on by the audacity of the challenge, the divine council quickly accepts, fully confident that this contest will display the utter might of the gods. To stand a chance against the mighty heavens, Brunhild will need to assemble history's greatest individuals, otherwise the death knell will surely be sounded for mankind.

details.Synonyms: Shuumatsu no Valkyrie, Valkyrie of the End

title: Ali Baba 2 Suoluomen Fengyin
synopsis: After leaving the treasure house world, Alibaba (voiced by Ding Yan), Margina (voiced by Ye Fang) and Xiaozhizhi (voiced by Sun Ke) once again joined hands on a new journey. This time, their goal was to find the long-lost treasure of Solomon, and Alibaba accidentally obtained an ancient book that recorded the hidden location of the treasure. However, in the process of searching for the treasure, Ali Baba accidentally broke the seal that restricted the devil, making the devil haunt the world again. The devil, who has been imprisoned for hundreds of years, is full of anger and desire for revenge. He wants to recover everything from humans. 　　 In order to make up for their mistakes, Alibaba and his team began to look for a sealed bottle that could re-seal the devil. What they didn't expect was that the sealed bottle fell into the hands of their old rival robber trio.(translated from douban)

title: Zhongguo Changshi Ban
synopsis: "Yuan Ri" uses ancient poems as the background and uses the eyes of a child to see the traditions and customs of the Spring Festival in Jiading of the Ming Dynasty 400 years ago. In the sound of firecrackers, the children played in groups, the fathers used wooden ladders to post spring festival couplets and hung lanterns, and the mothers were busy in the kitchen for a sumptuous New Year meal. The child came to the kitchen to steal food, but was caught by his father, who used traditional etiquette and good manners. In the countryside and fields, there are also many people who bring carriages to pay New Year's greetings. A bowl of "Lunar New Year Soup" for hospitality, blending simplicity and tenderness, conveys the flavor of the Spring Festival in ancient times. 　　 "Lovesickness" tells the story of Tong'er (full name Wang Chutong), a young man with long braids in the Qing Dynasty, and Liu Niang, a childhood sweetheart, and a love affair with red beans when they were young. After growing up, the boy and Liu Niang had no choice but to pass by because of improper households. Later, Liu Niang was forced to marry the rich young master, and was no longer able to stay with the young man in her heart. The boy who lost his love waited for his fame and left his hometown on a small boat with a handkerchief embroidered by Liuniang with a red bean pattern. 　　 "Wandering Zi Yin" is based on the story of Wang Mingsheng, a Qing historian and classicist, presents a universal story of motherhood for thousands of years. It also allows "travelers" who are usually busy with work to learn from the stories of characters in traditional culture. In the animated short film "Drinking Lake at the First Time and Rain", classic ancient poems are sung in the form of ballads, lingering on the Mid-Autumn Festival night of the Ming Dynasty. In my heart, sent a bright and bright moon. 　　 The short film "Night Thoughts" tells the story of Gu Weijun, a famous diplomat of Jiading origin in 1932, as the only Chinese representative of the League of Nations investigation team, went to the northeast to investigate the "September 18th" incident and the establishment of the pseudo-Manchukuo.   --Baidu baike(translated from douban)

title: Chouxiaoya Lixian Ji
synopsis: Ah Ni, a "robot duck" from the moon, was adopted by the mother duck of the prairie flying duck family by chance. Ah Ni firmly believes that like other ducklings, he is eager to spread his wings and fly. 　　 The super chip on Ah Ni's body has attracted lunar people to track. It turns out that Ah Ni is a super bomb used by evil scientists on the moon to destroy the earth's atmosphere. Under the chase of the coyotes, Ah Ni and his friends went south to reunite with the migrating ducks. Regardless of the danger of chip explosion, Ah Ni finally defeated the evil doctor and helped the ducks to reach the south victoriously by virtue of love and affection and bravery. 　　 And Ah Ni realized his dream: to grow into a real little flying duck. (translated from douban)

title: Chaoji You Eryuan
synopsis: Legend has it that in a corner of the world, there is a mysterious place called "Super Kindergarten." 　　 Song Xiaocong is very naughty and likes pranks, which makes all kindergarten teachers and nanny a headache. After waking up one morning, Xiao Cong discovered that he and his friends had come to this strange place-the super kindergarten. The hilarious adventure of the little guys kicked off. What will be waiting for them in front? (translated from douban)

title: Tai Di Xiong Zhi Wanju Dazhan
synopsis: The evil Dr. Wu (voiced by Bai Wenxian), in order to let his invented high-tech VR toys monopolize the childhood of all children, formulated a conspiracy to destroy all traditional plush and mecha toys. The cute and shy Teddy Bear (voiced by Deng Xiaoting) didn't want to participate in this matter, but under the strong pull of the mech fighter Xiao Fei (voiced by Bai Wenxian), he strayed into an adventure and finally saved the toy world. (translated from douban)

title: Si Du Chishui
synopsis: Using animation documentary techniques, a wonderful historical story during the Red Army’s Long March is reproduced, fully demonstrating "the bravery of the Red Army, the god of soldiers, and the greatness of spirit". 　　 The film truly shows the historical events that the Central Red Army experienced during the Long March, such as the Battle of Xiangjiang, the Zunyi Conference, the Crossing of Chishui River, and the rush to cross the Jinsha River.(translated from douban)

title: Qingwa Zongdongyuan
synopsis: The frog family lives in a large swamp with a picturesque and pleasant climate. They have reproduced here for generations and lead a peaceful and happy life. However, one day, a group of bullfrogs who didn't know where they came from appeared in the swamp and broke the peace that was shrouded here. In the fierce battle, the frog Xiao Heimeng (voiced by Ji Jing) unfortunately separated from his mother. Humans want to build a factory next to the swamp, which is bound to have a devastating blow to the ecology of the swamp. In order to survive, the frog family decided to move the family to find a new home, and Xiao Heimeng was also trapped in the huge In the team, move forward. In this process, Xiao Heimeng not only has to face the frequent accidents and dangers around, but also finds the whereabouts of her mother and returns to her mother. Faced with the eager enemies and erratic fate, Xiao Heimeng can finally complete Is this difficult task?(translated from douban)

title: Xin Mu Ou Qiyu Ji
synopsis: A disobedient wooden man was brought back to the human world by the carpenter for teasing the carpenter and carved into a puppet. He named Pinocchio. He was naughty and playful and fell into a puppet theater. He was deceived into a toy country and turned into a donkey. Finally, he reunited with his father in the belly of a shark , And successfully escaped and returned home for a period of fantasy adventure. (translated from douban)

title: Rexue Leifeng Xia Zhi Jiqing Yingjiu
synopsis: Zheng Yi is an ordinary college student, but he has a full sense of justice. His wish is to become a bicycle stuntman and win the Grand Prix. An accident made him meet a girl named Chen Yang. Pan Ran is Zheng Yi’s good friend. He who loves to eat roadside stalls turned into a ditch oil monster because he ate too much ditch oil, and went around doing evil. However, there was a fierce battle in the streets and lanes. In the end, Zheng Yi defeated Pan Ran and saved a baby. His feat was filmed and posted on the Internet. People called Zheng Yi Lei Fengxia. 　　 Over time, a spark of love collided between Zheng Yi and Chen Yang, while at the same time, the toy store owner Shen Mo was planning an evil conspiracy. In the face of a cunning enemy, can Zheng Yi once again show the style of Lei Fengxia? (translated from douban)

title: Ciwei Xiao Zi Zhi Tiansheng Wo Ci
synopsis: Big Hedgehog (voiced by Su Shangqing) is a brave and happy little hedgehog. Although he often causes troubles of all sizes due to his impulsive personality, he is still deeply trusted and loved by friends. In an accident, the hedgehog lost his memory, so he and his friend A Hui (voiced by Tang Shuiyu) embarked on a journey to find himself. 　　 On the way, the two met the kind-hearted human Xiao Ming (voiced by Lu Zhixing). The kind-hearted Xiao Ming is committed to animal protection. He has repeatedly helped the hedgehog out of trouble, and the two have forged a deep friendship. A Mei (voiced by Yan Mengmeng) is the daughter of the leader of Hedgehog Valley. This unexpected journey also sparked a spark between her and the hedgehog. The evil and greedy Doctor Thinkman used Xiao Ming's love for animals to realize his ambitions. The hedgehog discovered the doctor's conspiracy. How can it defeat this powerful enemy? (translated from douban)

title: Fengkuang Chouxiaoya
synopsis: There is a beautiful bird kingdom in a distant place, but the tranquility here is soon broken by the rebellion of the opposition, and the parents of the Ugly Duckling (voiced by Su Qianyun) mysteriously disappeared to protect the Liuli Bird. In order to understand the secret of Liuliniao and find his parents, Ugly Duckling and his good friend Ugly Xiaoba (voiced by Wang Xueqin) embarked on a journey to find the old cat mage, but they did not know that the danger came quietly. 　　 Under the agitation of the opposition, the birds launched a war against mankind. In order to prevent the further expansion of the war, the ugly duckling with the secret of heaven resolutely boarded the Liuli Tower. What will be waiting for him in front... (translated from douban)

title: Shuiguo Baobei
synopsis: The fruit babies are fighting wits and courage with the evil insects every day, and the joining of a pair of behemoths caused an uproar and led the fruit babies into various magical and magical adventures. The fruit babies also have a new member blueberry to join. The energetic fruit babies, evil worms and mysterious creatures stage new stories. After a series of tests, the fruit babies become the real heroes of the fruit village, and the fruit babies are growing. (translated from douban)

title: Shuiguo Baobei Zhi Shuiguo Zongdongyuan
synopsis: The film tells the story of the little orange lucky star growing into a fruit hero in order to defend the fruit village. Ji Xing lives in a mysterious village hidden in the lush forest. The name of the village is Fruit Village, where the villagers are not disturbed by the outside world and live happily. In this day's class, Teacher Tao talked about the evil worms coming out of the forest and attacking Fruit Village 30 years ago. After school, Ji Xing, who wanted to be a fruit hero, was very excited about the existence of "villagers", gathered friends and walked into the forest together. In the forest, Ji Xing found that the evil worm reappeared and knocked down the evil worm with the help of his companions. Since then, the evil worms reappeared, and the offensive and defensive battle between fruit and evil worms has begun! Back in the Fruit Village, Ji Xing and his team told everyone that the worm has reappeared! In order to resist the worms, the fruits began to build walls. On the side of the evil worm, the giant witch insect sent a color-changing insect to spy on the enemy, but the color-changing insect was easily defeated by the lucky star, canna and the star. The chameleon returned to the evil worm base to report the condition of the wall, and Dr. Chong began to develop tools to destroy the wall. The next day, all the evil worms used Dr. Worm’s props to cross the wall and attack the Fruit Village. At the same time, a mysterious monster also appeared in the Fruit Village. (translated from douban)

title: Maxiaole Zhi Wanju Ye Fengkuang
synopsis: Like all elementary school students, Ma Xiaole (voiced by Li Jiayi) always feels that there is too much homework to do and too little time for playing. In order to urge Ma Xiaole to study, his father, who loves invention and creation, also made a smart toy called "Big Head" (voiced by Li Xiaomeng). He followed Ma Xiaole's buttocks all day, making him annoying. 　　In an accident, Ma Xiaole met the elf little yellow hat (voiced by Zhao Huishan), and soon, the same innocent and kind two became friends. Little Yellow Cap thinks that Ma Xiaole should enjoy a carefree and happy childhood, instead of being overwhelmed by homework every day. Therefore, it has started a close match with the big head. The little yellow cap was losing to the big head and he was about to lose. At this moment, the little yellow cap took Ma Xiaole into the time tunnel and crossed back to the past. (translated from douban)

title: Platinum End
synopsis: After the death of his parents, a young Mirai Kakehashi is left in the care of his abusive relatives. Since then, he has become gloomy and depressed, leading him to attempt suicide on the evening of his middle school graduation. Mirai, however, is saved by a pure white girl named Nasse who introduces herself as a guardian angel wishing to give him happiness—by granting him supernatural powers and a chance to become the new God. In order to earn the position, he must defeat 12 other "God Candidates" within 999 days. Soon, Mirai begins a struggle to survive as a terrifying battle royale erupts between himself and the candidates looking to obtain the most power in the world.

Naturally, students of the Fashion Kingdom’s Fashion Academy cannot miss this golden opportunity. By chance, the pair of trousers and Sisi, who had failed the exam, got into the palace. After they set off a farce in the palace, they unexpectedly won the title of "Star Designer". (translated from douban)

Therefore, the two sides launched a funny and philosophical battle around the world. In the end, the five elements of ants regained the spirit orbs, allowing Chinese culture to shine on the earth, and the earth has become more beautiful. With a dream, the little ant flies to the next stop in the universe. (translated from douban)

synopsis: The self-righteous little ape (voiced by Lu Peiyu) disrupted the tribe’s annual hunting. However, the horrible bug in the legend made the fathers uncomfortable, and the father of the female man Ling Ding (voiced by Wang Susu) failed to even return to the tribe. In order to prove himself, the little ape disregarded the ban of the tribe, the strict rules of the elders, and the obstruction of his friends, and resolutely rushed to the forest with a bell. At this time, the ferocious bird is planning a revenge against the tribe. On the night of the full moon, can the little apes and bells who have experienced the test of life and death find their father? Will the little ape still stick to the bell when he encounters the scary bug in the legend? In the face of a tribe caught in vengeance attacks, can children perform miracles?(translated from douban)

title: Dong Zhiwu Dazhan
synopsis: In the fantastic Songsong Town, animals and plants can communicate with each other, which is novel and natural. The new squirrels, Songsong and Lele, use the leaf glasses given by the god tree grandfather to observe a world invisible to the naked eye-the underground root forest covered by layers of rock and soil is hidden under the epidermis of plants The magical energy flow... 　　 The arrival of Uncle Beard, who opened a paper mill, broke the calm of Songsong Town. Large areas of precious red pine forest were swallowed by tree-eating robots and turned into raw materials. The sewage pipes of the buried factories continuously discharged sewage and garbage underground. The discharge of a large amount of pollution has formed a powerful pollution monster. The pollution monster is destroying Songsong Town under the ground. Songsong Lele leads the little rabbit Beibei, the little flying squirrel flying, the little monkey Munk, and the little fat mouse card. Ka formed a small team to defend the town, and the plants joined hands to help each other, and an animal and plant counterattack began. Songsong used acorn shells and large leaves to make a small plane that can spray plant cannonballs. He also used pumpkins and rattans to form a plant tank. He also used the characteristics of spraying melons to create anti-aircraft cannons. The energy for all this is the photosynthesis of plants effect…… 　　 During the fierce battle, due to the continuous emission of pollution from the factory, Uncle Beard also reaped the consequences. The stratum under the small factory was corroded to form a hollow, and eventually collapsed. Uncle Beard’s life was also at risk... 　　 Whether to persist in destroying the pollution monsters or to save the life of Uncle Beard, a choice of life and death is placed in front of the residents of Songsong Town...(translated from douban)

Jixiang Bao worked diligently with the principal to practice cooking. As time went by, he gradually achieved success. In a cooking competition, he won the first place and got the participation. Qualification for the Food Emperor Cup God of Cooking Competition means that Jixiang baby will meet more and more powerful opponents. Can he beat them when he is not mature enough?
